#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn22.118"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.118:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.118:0.2"
msgid "12. Dhammakathikavagga "
msgstr "12. A Dhamma speaker "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 118. Paripucchitasutta → parimucchita 1 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn22.118:0.3"
msgid "118. Paripucchitasutta "
msgstr "118. Questioning "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.166, sc1
msgctxt "sn22.118:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.118:1.2"
msgid "“Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "“What do you think, mendicants? "

msgctxt "sn22.118:1.3"
msgid "rūpaṃ ‘etaṃ mama, esohamasmi, eso me attā’ti samanupassathā”ti? "
msgstr "Do you regard form like this: ‘This is mine, I am this, this is my self’?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.118:1.4"
msgid "“No hetaṃ, bhante”. "
msgstr "“No, sir.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.118:1.5"
msgid "“Sādhu, bhikkhave. "
msgstr "“Good, mendicants! "

msgctxt "sn22.118:1.6"
msgid "Rūpaṃ, bhikkhave, ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya daṭṭhabbaṃ. "
msgstr "Form should be truly seen with right understanding like this: ‘This is not mine, I am not this, this is not my self.’ "

msgctxt "sn22.118:1.7"
msgid "Vedanaṃ … "
msgstr "Do you regard feeling … "

msgctxt "sn22.118:1.8"
msgid "saññaṃ … "
msgstr "perception … "

msgctxt "sn22.118:1.9"
msgid "saṅkhāre … "
msgstr "choices … "

msgctxt "sn22.118:1.10"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ ‘etaṃ mama, esohamasmi, eso me attā’ti samanupassathā”ti? "
msgstr "consciousness like this: ‘This is mine, I am this, this is my self’?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.118:1.11"
msgid "“No hetaṃ, bhante”. "
msgstr "“No, sir.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.118:1.12"
msgid "“Sādhu, bhikkhave. "
msgstr "“Good, mendicants! "

msgctxt "sn22.118:1.13"
msgid "Viññāṇaṃ, bhikkhave, ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya daṭṭhabbaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "Consciousness should be truly seen with right understanding like this: ‘This is not mine, I am not this, this is not my self.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.118:1.14"
msgid "evaṃ passaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "Seeing this … "

msgctxt "sn22.118:1.15"
msgid "nāparaṃ itthattāyāti pajānātī”ti. "
msgstr "They understand: ‘… there is no return to any state of existence.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.118:1.16"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

